items.text:
We are casting for the 2026 Weird and Wonderful festival which will run between March 3rd and March 8th.

‚ÄúSardines‚Äù follows five sardines as they bicker over life's meaning and their purpose in the world. 

We are looking for 5 actors of any age or look who can comfortably play off of each others comedic timing.

If you are interested in auditioning for a role please send a self tape that you feel fits the criteria via we transfer / any other downloadable link to:

Seanrobinsonfreelance@gmail.com

Self tapes are due by 31st December and the cast will be contacted by the new year.

Please note: this is a 20 min play and will be part of a three play evening. A profit share will be paid.

I Wear The Mask Audition üé≠üé≠ 

Saturday , December 13th
Location: Online‚ÄîZoom
Time: 9am -11am - Please note all auditions will be given a specific time within this frame
Show Date: February 21st at 5:00pm PST
Location: Oakland, California 
Online rehearsals start December 22nd @ 6pm
Contract: $125

 Submit headshot and resume to puturplayon.com/casting-call

Seeking-‚Äî
 
BRADFORD/DESHAWN: Black male. Early to late 20‚Äôs with a beautiful body. As Bradford, he is articulate and upper-middle class. As DeShawn, he pretends to be thuggish and mumbling. Bradford is struggling with being a part of the upper middle class while trying to learn about his culture.

I Wear the Mask is the challenge faced by Bradford/DeShawn depending on who is wearing the mask. Bradford struggles to hide the pain and suffering of being Black in the late 90‚Äôs and hides his true feelings behind a fa√ßade of joy and contentment to navigate racial justice in and out of his community.

Quietly building.

This certificate represents one of many programs completed as part of Tony Robbins‚Äô AI Advantage training. It‚Äôs one layer in what amounts to months of research, testing, and development behind The Actors Copilot.

Actors don‚Äôt need surface-level tools or borrowed frameworks.
They need systems that understand craft, psychology, pressure, and lived experience.

Every course taken, including this one, has been run through a single filter:
Does this materially help actors prepare better, make clearer choices, and show up with truth?

If it doesn‚Äôt translate directly into the work actors actually do ‚Äî auditions, self-tapes, character preparation, and long-term career thinking ‚Äî it doesn‚Äôt make the cut.

The work continues.
Carefully. Thoughtfully. 
@theactorscopilot

Looking for your dream home in a fantastic neighborhood? I just toured this gem on Whitney Road West in Fairport, and let me tell you, it‚Äôs a standout. With its blend of modern updates and timeless charm, this three-bedroom, two-bath home is ready to win your heart. Nestled right in the heart of Fairport, it‚Äôs got everything from a beautifully renovated kitchen to a cozy living room with a fireplace and a sunroom that‚Äôs perfect for any season.

Why Fairport? This town isn‚Äôt just a place to live; it‚Äôs a community where you‚Äôll feel right at home, with great local amenities and a welcoming atmosphere.

Feel free to reach out to me if you want to take a look‚ÄîI‚Äôd love to show you around!

items.text:
The Play Society launches this Summer in Paris! 

Train with celebrated teachers from around the world in acting and performance-making, rooted in an ethos of play and collaboration. 

Our faculty represents the finest acting training programs in the world (Yale School of Drama, NYU, The Actors Center, l'Ecole Jacques Lecoq), works for renowned artists/companies (Pig Iron, Meredith Monk), and has taught many of today's most thrilling contemporary actors, directors, writers and creators - Lupita Nyong'o, Louisa Jacobson (Guilded Age, The Materialists), Winston Duke (Black Panther), yao (Sinners). 

Join us for two dedicated weeks with an international cohort of artists to refine your tools for rigorous play, bold imagination and skillful collaboration & co-creation -- training to enhance your presence on stage or screen, to work from and enlarge your pleasure in playing, and to bring specificity, artistry and authenticity to your storytelling. 

www.theplaysociety.org 

Registration is open now. Limited Scholarships available.

Hi everyone,
I‚Äôm Mohamed Redha Zertal, Liverpool-based with a strong on-camera presence and real performance experience. 
I‚Äôm looking to collaborate on short films, drama pieces, and character-led projects across Liverpool, Manchester, and Salford.

What I bring:
‚Ä¢ Strong screen presence
‚Ä¢ Stand-up comedy experience (Hot Water Comedy Club)
‚Ä¢ Confident delivery + natural timing
‚Ä¢ Multilingual: Arabic, French, English
‚Ä¢ Athletic look ‚Äî ideal for police, detective, action, villain, father, security, or emotional drama roles
‚Ä¢ Reliable, disciplined, takes direction well
‚Ä¢ Comfortable with emotional scenes and dialogue-heavy roles

Availability:
‚Ä¢ Immediate
‚Ä¢ Flexible for rehearsals & shoot days
‚Ä¢ Same-day self-tapes

I can provide:
‚Ä¢ Professional headshots
‚Ä¢ 20‚Äì30 sec intro/showreel clip
‚Ä¢ Self-tape for any role
‚Ä¢ Full acting CV

If you need someone who shows up prepared, delivers, and treats your film seriously, feel free to message me.

Looking forward to working with talented filmmakers.
‚Äì Redha üé¨

items.title: Hi everyone,

items.text:
URGENT Casting Call

For upcoming Non-Union Series, ANCIENT BODIES SEASON 2.

Looking for 

* Latino/Hispanic or Indigenous/ First Nations Males, 30 - 49 yrs, with Medium length to Long hair, Lean or Athletic build (No Tattoos)

Non-Union Only
Rate: $200 per day
Manitoba Residents Only (MUST have SIN #) 
Filming in Winnipeg and the surrounding areas
Must be available December 16 & 17 and must have full day and evening availability both days

Please email info@oafilmstudio.com with the subject line: 

* Male 40s_YOUR NAME

Include the following info:ÔøΩ
- Full Name
- Age
- Gender
- Ethnicity
- Height
- Phone
- Email Address
- State that you are non-union and a Manitoba resident with a SIN# and work permit
- Your availability December 16 & 17 (Must be available all day and evening both days)
- State if you have tattoos
- Do you have your own transportation or a reliable ride?
- If you have any acting or performance experience, let us know (Speaking, SOC, Background, Theatre, Public speaking, Social Media). No experience is alright.
- 2 Current (TAKEN DAY OF SUBMISSION) Photos (1 selfie & 1 Full Body Shot)

Please share!

#Winnipeg #winnipegcastingcall #WinnipegActing

items.text:
WINTER CASTING MEET AND GREET 

Join us on Friday, December 12 from 3:30 PM to 5:30 PM for another Casting Meet & Greet with Onalee Ames Film Studio Casting Crew! 

You are welcome to drop in quickly to fill out our casting form and have your photo taken to join the Onalee Ames Film Studio Casting database in preparation for Ancient Bodies S2 and all upcoming projects with Farpoint Films. 

All genders, ages, and experiences are welcome to drop in. 

If you are already part of the Onalee Ames Film Studio Casting Database, no need to come unless you would like to update your information.

Casting Meet & Greet
Friday, December 12, 2025
3:30 PM to 5:30 PM
LOCATION: ONALEE AMES FILM STUDIO
150 Stafford St, WINNIPEG, MB (through the pink door)

Please share!

üé¨ CASTING CALL | PAID CAMPAIGN | 'TWO NEEDS, ONE PLAN' üé¨

Hi everyone,

We are currently casting for a small, warm and family-oriented campaign titled ‚ÄúTwo Needs, One Plan‚Äù and are looking for a South Asian / Indian male actor, aged 60‚Äì75, to play the role of a Grandfather.

Role: Grandfather
Age: 60‚Äì75
Ethnicity: South Asian / Indian
Vibe: Warm, expressive, natural presence
Shoot: 1 day in or around Bedfordshire, Hertfordshire, or London (Date TBC ‚Äì ideally December 2025)
Fee: ¬£175 ‚Äì ¬£200 (flat fee)

Includes:
‚úÖ Reasonable travel expenses will be reimbursed, with mileage calculated using the fuel cost calculator from [FleetNews.co.uk](http://fleetnews.co.uk/) (UK average Pence per litre), or equivalent public transport fares.
‚úÖ Food will be provided during shoot hours.
‚úÖ Professional production

Company will possess unlimited usage rights across all platforms.

If you fit the brief, or know someone who does, please send the following to [michelle@universaltvmedia.com](mailto:michelle@universaltvmedia.com):
* Headshot
* Showreel, online professional profile, or previous work
* Current available & unavailable dates in December
* Confirmation of day rate within the stated range
* Your email and phone number

Please feel free to tag or share with actors in your network who might be interested.

We look forward to seeing your submissions and collaborating with talented performers from this community!

#castingcalls #asianactors #ukactors #paidgigs #casting #southasianactors #actoropportunity

CASTING/CREW CALL ‚Äì NEW DOCUMENTARY (Los Angeles, Jan/Feb 2026) 
ÔøΩFrom a TV Producer with Discovery & History Channel credits. 

I‚Äôm currently casting for a new documentary that explores the powerful stories we attach to the objects we treasure most. I‚Äôm looking for people who have one meaningful item something that, when held, brings back emotion, memory, or a story that shaped who you are.

Your object could be:
* A family heirloom
* A gift from someone who has passed
* A reminder of a relationship or life-changing moment
* Or simply something that holds deep, personal significance

This project will highlight everyday people and the extraordinary stories behind the things they hold dear.

FILMING:ÔøΩLos Angeles ‚Äî January & February 2026
If you have an item that carries emotional weight and a story you're willing to share on camera, I‚Äôd love to hear from you.

TO APPLY:ÔøΩPlease get in touch and share a brief description of yourself, your item, and the story behind it. Photos welcome but not required.
Looking forward to hearing your story.

EMAIL: breynolsbri@gmail.com
INSTAGRAM: @bryannareynolds

Faster prep.

topComments.text: Join a local Amateur Dramatics society to find out if you CAN act, as it is a talent that not everyone possesses.  Then, if you‚Äôre any good, get some professional training, a show reel, good headshots and apply to lots of agents for representation.

I started my acting journey at 50. After some extra work, i realised wanted speaking parts, so I i auditioned for a screen acting course - as I wanted feedback/coaching. I then got professional headshos and started with setting up a profile on Mandy, for me unpaid student films were a great training ground and I also got paid work for social media adverts. From there i expanded onto Backstage, Star Now and Talent Talks. The paid work I got booked for enabled me to get onto Spotlight and get an agent. All little steps towards my dream. Lots of learning on the way, such as how to self tape. Good luck

Kostium jest  na konkretny wymiar a osoba grajƒÖca tego ≈ºo≈Çnierza bƒôdzie zmiennikiem innego o podobnych parametrach jak na zdjƒôciach. W projekcie planujemy 6 odcink√≥w w tym po≈Çowa z nich jest z ≈ºo≈Çnierzami.

**Na wiosnƒô roku 2026 planujemy realizacje zdjƒôc do tego **projektu. Bƒôdziemy realizowaƒá mini serial oparty o wƒÖtki grupy okultystycznej ‚Äô‚Äô**Ahnenerbe‚Äô**‚Äô kt√≥ra chce zdobyƒá s≈Çynne artefakty ale w tym kto≈õ im chce przeszkadzaƒá. Projekt bƒôdzie  siƒô sk≈Çadaƒá z 6 odcink√≥w po 10/12 minut ka≈ºdy. Bƒôdziemy te≈º sukcesywnie dodawaƒá inne og≈Çoszenia zwiƒÖzane z tym projektem. Mile widziane zdjƒôcia aktualne. Na zdjƒôciu powy≈ºej osoba bƒôdzie mieƒá podobny kostium.** **Umieszczone materia≈Çy sƒÖ z naszej sesji.** Nie bƒôdzie to zlecenie p≈Çatne.**

 

Od 01.04.25 za≈Ço≈ºyli≈õmy sw√≥j kana≈Ç na portalu youtube z filmami z naszych plan√≥w ≈ºeby mo≈ºna by≈Ço zobaczyƒá jak to u nas wyglƒÖda od kuchni.

Wiƒôcej informacji na Priv

**Serial nie jest stworzony z sympatii do tej nazistowskiej organizacji lecz wynika to z samego scenariusza aby ukaza≈Ç zbrodnie i sam fakt i≈º by≈Ça w pe≈Çni z≈Ça. W produkcji znajdƒÖ siƒô osoby, kt√≥re bƒôdƒÖ chcieƒá walczyƒá i potƒôpiaƒá te wielkie z≈Ço jakim by≈Ç nazizm. sharedPost.text:
Casting call for "People"
We are casting for the 2026 Weird and Wonderful festival which will run between March 3rd and March 8th.

"People" follows Alex (a delivery driver) and his brief encounter delivering fish and chips to a Genie. What will he wish for?

Genie: 

We are looking for a male presenting actor with a playing age of 40-50s. This character needs to be larger than life, think someone that could easily play a jolly Santa Claus. The actor must feel comfortable having a strong command of the stage.

Alex: 

We are looking for a male presenting actor with a playing age in their 20s. The actor playing Alex will also need to have lived experience of living as an LGBT individual and comfortable discussing this struggle on stage.

If you are interested in auditioning for either role please send a self tape that you feel fits the character via we transfer / any other downloadable link to:

sineadrenaye@gmail.com

Self tapes are due by 22nd December and the cast will be contacted by the new year.

Please note: this is a 20 min play and will be part of a three play evening. A profit share will be paid.

Plastic Monkey Films UK (www.plasticmonkeyfilms.com) is seeking actors to fill roles for their third feature film, written and directed by Scott McQuaid *(‚ÄòSpace Ninjas‚Äô, ‚ÄòThe Heartsmith‚Äô, as seen on Amazon Prime, Apple TV+, and Tubi.)*

Set and shot in England, the film surrounds a writer and a painting. Filming for these roles will commence in Essex & London, in end-July to August 2026.

Please ensure you are based in England and are able to travel to Essex and London with relative ease. 

More info in the graphic below. Please apply via email by sending your headshot and any other relevant information to producer.plasticmonkeyfilms@gmail.com by 15th December 2025. Selected candidates will be contacted.

Thank you! 

Warmest regards,

Alexandria Kay

Producer at Plastic Monkey Films

I tested my own book today‚Ä¶ on a TERRIBLE script.
And the result honestly blew me away. üî•

I took a chapter from The Trinity Acting Method into class and watched my actors take a flat, clunky, uninspired script and lift it off the page ‚Äî turning it into something genuinely brilliant.

That‚Äôs what happens when actors have a method designed for real auditions, real results, and real transformation.

If one chapter can do that‚Ä¶ imagine what the whole book can do for your acting. üëÄüé¨

items.text:
PURPLE DREAMS PRODUCTIONS are looking for several performers to join a few projects, primarily our brand new family-friendly play: 

THE PRINCESS & THE KNIGHT

a fantasy play written by Tobias Nicholls

Welcome to Twinklewood, a fantastical land where darkness and light have lived in harmony for decades‚Ä¶ until now.

Whilst the King is away on a royal tour, the Ruler of the Shadow Realm makes an unexpected appearance. Sir Milo is determined to keep his princess safe, but with her Kingdom thrown into chaos, Princess Nova - who has long dreamt of adventure - springs into action, taking them on a journey up to the highest mountain and down to the deepest, darkest cave.

Battles are fought and lessons learned on this funny and exciting quest.  

This brand new production is set to debut at The Seagull Theatre in Lowestoft on Saturday 4th April 2026

Two performances on the one day as a tester before we look at booking any others. 

The script is currently going through a rewrite, with the intention to have the cast help to develop the characters through the rehearsal process with the director. 

Adding to the fantastical nature of the story, the characters of Twinklewood will all feature likenesses to animals - realised through costume and make-up.  Aside from one, roles have not been assigned any particular animal, allowing the chosen actors can help build their character.

Payment: at this stage of development it‚Äôs best to consider this a profit share, although this could change to a flat fee - happy to have open and honest discussions with applicants. 

Rehearsals will take place at our studio in Hunstanton (PE36), and will be as flexible as possible to fit around other commitments.

If you are interested, or know someone that might be, please get in touch via a DM on here, or email purple-dreams@hotmail.co.uk

* 15+ Jahren Casting- & Kamera-Erfahrung
* Coaching von hunderten Darstellern

#schauspielworkshop #quereinsteiger #schauspielquereinsteiger #quereinsteigerworkshop #cameraacting #arbeitsworkshop #showreel #aboutme #film #tv #exklusiv #engelspostmanagement

Aufgrund der gro√üen Nachfrage veranstalte ich im JANUAR 2026 (09.-11.01.+16.-18.01.2026 / 2 WE) einen EXKLUSIVEN, 6-T√ÑGIGEN Schauspiel-Workshop f√ºr QUEREINSTEIGER*INNEN. Die Inhalte k√∂nnt Ihr dem Flyer entnehmen. 

Quereinsteiger*innen haben wenig M√∂glichkeiten auf dem deutschen Markt, weshalb ich mich dazu entschieden habe, ein sinnvolles, n√ºtzliches Angebot auf den Markt zu bringen. 

Es handelt sich um einen PRAXISORIENTIERTEN Workshop, was bedeutet, in welchem mit den Teilnehmenden an der Performance gearbeitet wird, u. a. durch Szenenarbeit, E-/Live-Casting-Situationen, Camera-Acting etc. Au√üerdem erhalten die Teilnehmenden alle wichtigen Informationen rund um das Thema "Selbstmarketing" - zusammen mit wertvollen Tipps und Tricks. 

Zus√§tzlich produzieren wir eine professionelle SHOWREELSZENE f√ºr jeden Teilnehmenden, welche wir in dem 6-t√§gigen Workshop vorbereiten (*WICHTIGE INFO: Die Produktion der Szenen findet au√üerhalb des Workshops statt. Die Termine werden im Anschluss individuell vereinbart!). des Weiteren erh√§lt jeder Teilnehmende ein kurzes "ABOUT ME", welches wir ebenfalls aufzeichnen werden. 

*Sollte f√ºr den Showreelszene eine erneute Anreise aus anderen St√§dten notwendig sein, werden die Fahrtkosten √ºbernommen.

ZIELGRUPPE: QUEREINSTEIGER*INNEN (ohne Ausbildung - unerfahren oder mit ersten Dreherfahrungen) sowie SCHAUSPIELSCH√úLER*INNEN, die ihre Ausbildung aktuell noch nicht abschlie√üen bzw. abgeschlossen haben.

INFOS & ANMELDUNG √ºber folgenden Link: [https://www.agentur-engelspost.de/workshops-coachings/workshops-und-weiterbildungen/schauspiel-workshop-quereinsteiger-innen-readyforacting/](https://www.agentur-engelspost.de/workshops-coachings/workshops-und-weiterbildungen/schauspiel-workshop-quereinsteiger-innen-readyforacting/)

New dates added - Dec 8-19 in Las Vegas. To book go to https://rebrand.ly/freehdsht

FREE HEADSHOT and 1-HOUR SESSION ‚Äì East Summerlin, Las Vegas

Address sent automatically after booking

Hi! I‚Äôm Steve Fogarty, a Las Vegas headshot specialist and owner of EXPO TRAFFIC, where we run large-scale headshot activations for major trade shows (600-700 people over 2.5 days).

I‚Äôm currently testing new lighting setups and posing flows for upcoming conventions, and I‚Äôm looking for real people to sit for practice sessions in a more relaxed environment. In return for your time, you get a full headshot session and one professional, retouched headshot for free.

**What You Get**
* A 60‚Äì75 minute headshot session
* Multiple looks + lighting setups
* A private online gallery
* One edited, retouched image included
* Additional images optional (zero pressure)

**Examples of my retouching**

[https://rebrand.ly/retouching](https://rebrand.ly/retouching)

Why There‚Äôs a $20 Fee

It‚Äôs not a sales charge. It‚Äôs a **non-refundable security deposit and show-up guarantee** that ensures the schedule stays reliable for both of us. The $20 simply confirms your commitment to attend ‚Äî and your favorite image is still included for free.

How You Get Your Image

After the session:
* We will review your images, and you'll tell me which ones are your favorites that you do not want deleted.
* I will edit and retouch your favorites, then upload them to your private gallery.
* You can download your favorite image using a coupon code (provided).
* You‚Äôre welcome to purchase extras, but it‚Äôs totally optional.

What to Expect / How to Prepare
* Arrive camera-ready (mirror + restroom available)
* Plan for 3‚Äì4 different looks
* Avoid pure white tops if possible
* Relax ‚Äî I‚Äôll guide you through every pose and expression

Safety + Professionalism
* All public areas are video security-monitored for your comfort and safety
* Private areas (bathrooms, changing areas) are never recorded
* References available by request

You can preview my work here:

[https://www.expotraffic.com/headshots/las-vegas-headshots](https://www.expotraffic.com/headshots/las-vegas-headshots)

**Location**

**East Summerlin near Rainbow & Alta**

**Exact address provided after booking.**

**Looking forward to creating something great together!**

**‚Äì Steve Fogarty**

**Owner ‚Äì STEVEN JOSEPH PHOTOGRAPHY | EXPO TRAFFIC HEADSHOTS**

Unpaid actor 

Hello. I am Grace, I am an ametur filmmaking, I am currently working on a mix media horror project called The Haven Institute. I am looking for a male actor to play the role of Young Nigel Harrow (AGE 20-23, set in 90s). This is currently as a backup so I have a range of actors to chose. What is required is that I will send over a block of script lasting around 3 minutes each (currently there are 7) and I will need the actor to film these clips in their time and their own environment. Location doesn't matter. This project is unpaid.

If you are interested or have any more questions please drop me an email at Thehollowreturn@outlook.com 

Diolch

Til et kortfilmsprojekt med arbejdstitlen ‚ÄúVISIT‚Äù s√∏ger vi 3 skuespillere til b√¶rende roller

üó∫Ô∏è AARHUS

üóìÔ∏è 5. - 10. FEBRUAR (+ bufferdag 11. februar)

FRIDA (Hovedrolle)

Spillealder: 22-28

MARCEL (Hovedrolle)

Spillealder: 20-28

DEN FREMMEDE (B√¶rende bi-rolle)

Spillealder: 24-30

OM FILMEN:

Frida og Marcel er begge midt i tyverne og er begge p√• hver sin m√•de g√•et i st√• i tilv√¶relsen. Frida f√∏ler, at hun sidder fast i sit ellers billedsk√∏nne og perfekte parforhold, og Marcel er lige blevet dumpet af pigen, han troede var sit livs k√¶rlighed.

I to parallelle handlingsforl√∏b kaster de sig ud i to vidt forskellige fors√∏g p√• at genfinde gnisten i den gr√• tilv√¶relse, p√• to forskellige dates, i to forskellige lejligheder p√• hver sin side af en opgang.

Vi er st√∏ttet af Aarhus Filmv√¶rksted, men er stadig en lavbudget-produktion drevet af passionerede frivillige. Projektet er derfor ikke l√∏nnet, men produktionen d√¶kker transport, samt m√•ltider og forfriskninger p√• set.

üìß Send en mail til [visitkortfilm@gmail.com](mailto:visitkortfilm@gmail.com) med titlen ‚ÄúCasting‚Äù efterfulgt af dit navn.
